  "name": "Transform Crab Dance!",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "4eFjWCvD5W22yFuT",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Sequin.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You shake your body to a phantom beat as chakra shrouds you, transforming you into a fiesty crab with pinchy...pinchers! While concentrating on this jutsu, you are unable to cast jutsu or make weapon attacks. Additionally, you gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>You count as one size smaller and gain a +3 bonus to your AC.</li><li>You are able to breathe underwater and gain a swimming speed equal to your movement speed.</li><li><p>As an action you may attempt to claw up an enemy, making a melee ninjutsu attack against an enemy within range. On a hit, you deal 3d4 slashing damage and grant 1 rank of bleeding. Alternatively, you can attempt to grapple your enemy, making the same attack roll but giving the Grappled condition on a successful hit. Affected creatures must make a Strength save against your Sequin DC.</p></li></ul><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> or each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the chakra cost by 3, and increase the damage by 1d4. If cast at B-rank or higher, creatures make the save at disadvantage.</p>",
